Turn right, go to the fridge. Stand in front of the fridge.
Open the refrigerator. Put the onion on the first level, left side. Close the door. Wait 7 seconds and open the door. Take out the onion. Close the door.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Place the onion on the left side of the sink.

Pick up the red onion nearest to the shelf from the table.
Turn right to head to the fridge.
Cool the onion in the fridge and take it out.
Turn right to walk to the sink.
Put the onion on the left sink.

high_descs: Head around and turn left and turn right move towards the coffeetable.

Place the onion inside the fridge, pick the onion from the fridge.
Turn right move towards the sink.
Place the onion on the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the onion on the sink.
